{"tid":1346791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毛主席說既話太對了","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:18:23.000Z","uid":30081,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed8b3362b1a321dd7f69a0b88a4163acc4be80e","tid":1346791,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"什麽叫工作，工作就是鬥爭。那些地方有困難、有問題，需要我們去解決。我們是為著解決困難去工作、去鬥爭的。越是困難的地方越是要去，這才是好同志。<br />\n<br />\n革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫綉花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，&ldquo;文質彬彬&rdquo;，那樣&ldquo;溫良恭儉讓&rdquo;。革命就是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動。<br />\n<br />\n世界是你們的，也是我們的，但是歸根結底是你們的。你們年青人朝氣蓬勃，正在興旺時候，好像早晨八、九點鍾的太陽。希望寄托在你們身上。 <br />\n<br />\n哪裏有壓迫，哪裏就有反抗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5435a5baa03faf863a9088c5b6885efa520709","tid":1346791,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣組 宣揚毛主席精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b419dafeac649b411133f1de89183946dc499cb","tid":1346791,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"毛主席萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7c607e1273a32a873084cb3b18a6f8fe784106","tid":1346791,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"召喚文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abda462042f55676df999d89e86a66f419a9cacf","tid":1346791,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:16:12.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6def56dbafbe7b3e861a8a660df647cb8f10668d","tid":1346791,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8815d80048d7e6b9465dbaa908460f4b629f71a","tid":1346791,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be64476529981da8a44f6d6f147369db608fefe2","tid":1346791,"uid":258421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"毛澤東名言佳句:<br />\n1. 世界是你們的，也是我們的，但是歸根結底是你們的。你們年青人朝氣蓬勃，正在興旺時候，好像早晨八、九點鍾的太陽。希望寄托在你們身上。 <br />\n2. 調查就象&quot;十月懷胎&quot;，解決問題就象&quot;一朝分娩&quot;。調查就是解決問題。(獨立調查)<br />\n3. 沒有調查就沒有發言權！(獨立調查)<br />\n4. 打得贏就打,打不贏就走。(be water)<br />\n5. 貪污和浪費是極大的犯罪！<br />\n6. 下定決心、不怕犧牲、排除萬難、去爭取勝利！<br />\n7. 如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。<br />\n8. 教育者必須先受教育。"}]}